## ✅ Phase 2: Docker Build & Test - COMPLETE

**Status**: Docker engine is running and local smoke test passed

**Completed**:
- Docker image built successfully: `mcb-app:v1`
- Container started successfully on port 5000
- Health endpoint validated: `{"status":"ok","service":"mathematically-correct-builds"}`

**Executed commands**:
```powershell
# Build image
"C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\resources\bin\docker.exe" build -t mcb-app:v1 .

# Test locally
"C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\resources\bin\docker.exe" run -p 5000:5000 -e FLASK_ENV=production -e PORT=5000 mcb-app:v1

# Verify health endpoint
python -c "import urllib.request; print(urllib.request.urlopen('http://127.0.0.1:5000/health').read().decode())"
```

